TextUtils.closeTags() does not handle self closing input fields.
E.g.
{code:java}
TextUtils.closeTags("<input type='submit' name='Nick'/>");
{code}

will produce:
{noformat}
"<input type='submit' name='Nick'/></input>"
{noformat}

This creates invalid html.  The only place I know that this can cause issues is in the introduction where we try to close off tags (not sure why).

